translation: 尸检报告：卡洛琳·希比尔

original: "Died at 2:18PM. Cause of death was suffocation. Her body was found floating in a nearby lake outside of the Grand Cathedral. \n \nTraces of transmutation, evocation, and necromancy magic were found on the body.”
translation: “死亡时间下午2:18。死因窒息。尸体被发现漂浮于大教堂外的湖面。\n\n尸体上发现了形变，塑能和死灵术的痕迹。
